Package: spatiotempDQN
Type: Package
Title: Spatio-Temporal CNN-LSTM DQN Toolkit for Multivariate Rewards and Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Jong-Min", family = "Kim", email = "kjonomi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jong-Min Kim <kjonomi@gmail.com>
Description: Utilities to simulate spatio-temporal data, build CNN-LSTM DQN models using keras,
    train with optional uncertainty-weighted sampling, evaluate off-policy with IPS,
    and run clustering and visualizations of CATE-like contrasts.
